    <item>
      <title>随着技术裁员的继续，TikTok 削减了 60 名销售和广告职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tiktok-cuts-60-employees-as-wave-of-tech-layoffs-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[字节跳动旗下的 TikTok 加入了科技公司的一系列裁员行列，裁员约 60 人，其中大部分在销售和广告部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tiktok-cuts-60-employees-as-wave-of-tech-layoffs-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:34:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAP 计划在 AI 领域重组 8,000 个岗位，上调 2025 年展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/sap-gives-profit-outlook-for-2025-unveils-restructuring-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SAP SE 正在计划进行重组，这将影响约 8,000 个工作岗位，并加强这家德国软件制造商对人工智能的关注。该公司预计明年营业利润将增至约 100 亿欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/sap-gives-profit-outlook-for-2025-unveils-restructuring-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 23:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马云购买阿里巴巴股票以示对陷入困境的帝国的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/alibaba-gains-on-report-ma-tsai-buy-200-million-in-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在亿万富翁联合创始人马云购买股票后，阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司(Alibaba Group Holding Ltd.)录得六个月来最大涨幅，这对一家经历了内部动荡和股市暴跌的公司来说是急需的提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/alibaba-gains-on-report-ma-tsai-buy-200-million-in-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
